data.description: Description:  Location! Location! Location! Welcome to this captivating 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in Tradd’s Landing. As you step through the front entrance, you’re greeted by a split floor plan. The living areas flow seamlessly providing a perfect balance of openness. Entertain guests in the formal dining area. The heart of this home is the spacious kitchen with a farmhouse chandelier and a cozy nook. The Family room provides a more relaxed everyday living. The master suite is a true retreat boasting a spa like ensuite bathroom, a closet, and a sliding door leading to the screened in back porch. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space with three hallway closets and four farmhouse flush mount ceiling lights. The oversize garage has built in shelves and a built-in work bench. The driveway has plenty of parking space. Tradd’s Landing amenities includes swimming pool, kid’s playground, and a Lake with a dock. The community pool is walking distance to enjoy the sun. Tradd’s Landing is nearby schools, stores, and restaurants, and a short distance to Disney and other attraction parks. What are you waiting for? Let me show you this home.    In order to ensure the Buyer is aware of the new law restricting certain real estate purchases by certain Foreign Buyers, we request Buyer signatures on the Foreign Buyer Notice (available in the attachments), to accompany all offers.”
